message.content: cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.COMM, cs.SY - This paper deals with the simulation and evaluation of a wireless backhaul solution for mmWave networks, which involves aspects of network infrastructure, communication protocols, and system-level performance analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.MM (Multimedia), which are relevant to the communication and signal processing aspects of the problem. Additionally, cs.COMM (Communications) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also possible categories, as they cover the broader topics of wireless networks and system-level modeling and optimization.
